      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://kids.kiddle.co/Harbor_Isle,_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Harbor Isle is a census‑designated place within Nassau County, part of the larger Town of Hempstead.",
